title: New Apartment- 2 Bedroom- Wakefield
posting_body: ['Complete remodel built from the ground up.', ' New oversized windows offer copious sunlight, new modern white kitchen cabinets with imported granite countertops offer plenty of counter space for the chef.', ' Brand new stainless steel appliances, double refrigerator with ice maker, 5 burner gas stove, Stainless dishwasher, Moen faucets and under counter lighting complete the kitchen.', ' Fully wired flat screen wall mounted HDMI/DSL ports in living area and in each bedroom.', ' Dimmable flush mount LED ceiling lighting throughout.', ' Ceiling fans and plenty of closet space complete the two bedrooms.', ' Imported Italian tile stand-up shower and tub.', ' New bathroom vanity with custom granite countertop.', ' Sleep safely knowing approved NFPA (National Fire Prevention Compliant) Fire Sprinkler System and associated Alarm System throughout entire building.', ' Second floor unit with separate side entrance.', ' Located less than one minute walk from the North Ave Commuter Rail.', ' Gas forced hot water tenant responsible for utilities.']
